'''Boboqueequee''' was a location in [[Hutt/Legends|Hutt]] mythology, probably associated with the underworld. A common [[Huttese/Legends|Huttese]] imprecation was "Rot in Boboqueequee!"

==Behind the scenes==
"Rot in Boboqueequee!" is one of several intentionally abstruse Huttese imprecations featured in the [[Star Wars: Jabba the Hutt|Jabba the Hutt]] series and is obviously the Huttese equivalent of "Burn in Hell!"

